    Defines the JSON sidecar manifest schema (original_filename, processed_at,
    file_size, sha256, mthd_header, track_count) and a build_manifest() helper
    that assembles it from a file path + optional extracted metadata. Adds
    read_mthd_header() to parse the 14-byte MThd chunk (format/ntrks/division)
    so callers can populate the header block.
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>
